Revision history for Tapper-Config

5.0.4     2018-09-20
        - default output dir for minion testruns

5.0.3     2016-11-11
        - default config for tapper_prc: tapper-client without path

5.0.2     2016-03-10
        - store actually used tapper config file in config itself
        - disable TAP::DOM caching in DB by default

5.0.1     2016-02-16
        - set default log4perl dirs to /tmp

5.0.0     2016-02-08
        - log4perl tweaks
        - database merge TestrunDB+ReportsDB->TestrunDB

4.1.3     2012-11-23
        - default config values for testing

4.1.2     2012-11-22
        - silence test log4perl

4.1.1     2012-11-19
        - dzil pluginbundle TAPPER
        - use $HOME/.tapper/tapper.cfg instead of $HOME/.tapper.cfg

4.1.0     2012-10-19
        - [FEAT] special config handling for multiple databases
        - [TEST] for new special db entries
        - default entries:
          - web.use_authentication
          - testplans.path

4.0.2     2012-06-04
        - test more lax on matching paths with slashes
          for better Windows support

4.0.1     2012-05-16
        - Added default configs for new features
        - drop too heavy test requirements
        - provide new clientpkg architecture 'local'
        - Carved out installer grub file
        - big Dist::Zilla roundhouse kick

2011-04-07  Steffen Schwigon  <steffen.schwigon@amd.com>

	* v3.0.10

	* [FIX] allow absolute path for log4perl config
	* adapt config defaults to new server name and dir layout
	* release version++ roundhouse kick

2010-03-30 Steffen Schwigon <steffen.schwigon@amd.com>

	* v3.0.4

	* distro maintenance
	* rework log4perl handling
	* message receiver logfile to /var/log

2011-03-08 Steffen Schwigon <steffen.schwigon@amd.com>

	* v3.0

	* added webserver name to config

	* try to force YAML versions

2011-03-02  Steffen Schwigon  <steffen.schwigon@amd.com>

	* v3.0

	* first public CPAN release
